Message: The IPMI Provider attempted to set the value of the 'LowerThresholdNonCritical' property of the 'NumericSensor' class.  While the BMC returned a success status; retrieval of the property from the BMC indicated that it did not change.  This might be an issue with the BMC; please contact your BMC Vendor for more information.

The IPMI Provider attempted to set the value of the 'UpperThresholdNonCritical' property of the 'NumericSensor' class.  While the BMC returned a success status; retrieval of the property from the BMC indicated that it did not change.  This might be an issue with the BMC; please contact your BMC Vendor for more information.
